---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="포항공과대학교 방송국 PBS">
  <main>
    <section class="min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center py-32">
      <p
        class="container mb-5 md:mb-9 text-center text-white/50 font-medium uppercase"
      >
        POSTECH Broadcasting System
      </p>
      <h1
        class="container mb-5 md:mb-12 text-center text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold lg:text-8xl leading-tight"
      >
        하나의 마음,<span class="hidden md:inline"> </span><br
          class="md:hidden"
        />하나의 소리.
      </h1>
      <p
        class="container mx-auto mb-5 md:mb-9 md:text-xl text-center text-white/75 break-words"
      >
        포항공과대학교 방송국 PBS는 포스테키안의 목소리를 기억하고 담아내는
        <br class="hidden md:inline" />
        포항공과대학교 총학생회 산하의 언론기구입니다.
      </p>
      <ul class="container flex justify-center gap-8 mx-auto mb-20">
        <li>
          <a
            class="link"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            target="_blank"
            href="https://www.youtube.com/c/포항공과대학교방송국PBS"
          >
            Youtube
          </a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a
            class="link"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            target="_blank"
            href="https://instagram.com/postechpbs_official"
          >
            Instagram
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="relative rounded-xl">
          <iframe
            class="mx-auto w-full aspect-video rounded-xl"
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/OjW2gV_xm1g?autoplay=1&mute=1&controls=0&modestbranding=1&playsinline=1"
            frameborder="0"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen></iframe>
          <div class="absolute bottom-0 bg-zinc-900/75 backdrop-blur-md w-full py-4 rounded-b-xl">
            <p class="px-4 text-white/50 text-xs font-medium uppercase">Featured</p>
            <h1 class="px-4 font-bold">
              2022 PBS MT V-LOG
            </h1>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style lang="postcss">
  .link {
    @apply text-rose-500 text-lg hover:underline;
  }
  .link::after {
    @apply content-["_↗"] align-text-top;
  }
</style>
